brz-css-mqf1he"><div class="brz-section__content brz-section--boxed brz-css-lk7qip brz-css-amvcwq" data-brz-custom-id="zvvxvhtucewxkpruidypzaokovdzymggukkw"><div class="brz-bg"><div class="brz-bg-color"></div></div><div class="brz-container brz-css-zw5mjs brz-css-cfqddu"><div class="brz-row__container brz-css-1xsht5r brz-css-1oiqncu" data-brz-custom-id="nezskjuitmsyqimihjzouszpwllerwaghasf"><div class="brz-row brz-css-kq1g4p brz-css-1jkkkg6 brz-css-2amuzw"><div class="brz-columns brz-css-o26tfp brz-css-1n25z9s" data-brz-custom-id="quzsojseddypbcbzwcagvrehdtnxjshjqqtz"><div class="brz-column__items brz-css-1j8s0bo brz-css-ch9oev"><div id="" class="brz-css-68up2x brz-css-hh2y0j brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-1doei8y brz-css-15vn40t" data-brz-custom-id="yddguwavzfhvtiotbzibsmnjnrxbhvtyqhrg"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><h2 class="brz-text-xs-center brz-lh-lg-1_2 brz-lh-sm-im-1_2 brz-lh-xs-im-1_2 brz-fs-lg-42 brz-fs-sm-im-35 brz-fs-xs-im-30 brz-ls-lg-m_1_5 brz-ls-sm-im-m_0_5 brz-ls-xs-im-m_0_5 brz-ff-montserrat brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-700 brz-fw-sm-im-700 brz-fw-xs-im-700 brz-css-tcWC_"><span class="brz-cp-color1">Iron Ore (Fe)</span></h2></div></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-68up2x brz-css-11nlide brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-1doei8y brz-css-1pmt59m" data-brz-custom-id="eaezayfkhngcezanqazfxwyjtnkmpsvjouru"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><p class="brz-ls-xs-0 brz-fw-xs-400 brz-lh-xs-1_2 brz-fs-xs-16 brz-text-xs-center brz-ff-ubuntu brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-300 brz-text-lg-justify brz-fs-sm-16 brz-lh-sm-1_2 brz-fw-sm-400 brz-ls-sm-0 brz-text-sm-left brz-ls-lg-m_1_5 brz-ls-sm-im-m_2 brz-ls-xs-im-m_2 brz-fs-lg-22 brz-lh-lg-1_2 brz-css-wkz0q"><span class="brz-cp-color1">Iron ore&nbsp;is the main source of pure iron&nbsp;for the world's&nbsp;iron&nbsp;and steel industries... It is therefore&nbsp;essential&nbsp;for the production of steel, which in turn is&nbsp;essential&nbsp;to maintain a strong industrial base. Almost all (98%)&nbsp;iron ore&nbsp;is used in steelmaking.</span></p></div></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-68up2x brz-css-1qwagqp brz-css-dhgmac brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-spacer brz-css-cnperg brz-css-1pfnlj"></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-68up2x brz-css-ckkz4a brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-icon-text brz-css-3xyog0 brz-css-m5v0w6" data-brz-custom-id="jiketjufpbcizleasuvwpumozqdqvpupfktd"><div class="brz-icon__container" data-brz-custom-id="ungiugaeroycdktogzonjitcccdsgsmmcijs"><span class="brz-icon brz-span brz-css-9ulzpx brz-css-17pfjat"><svg class="brz-icon-svg align-[initial]"><use href="/wp-content/plugins/brizy/public/editor-build/prod/editor/icons/outline/scale-4.svg#nc_icon"></use></svg></span></div><div class="brz-text-btn"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-1doei8y brz-css-1wnuxlf" data-brz-custom-id="gxqurclnspsvjrnpmuvfzrpoisdkpakelgsq"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><h5 class="brz-mb-lg-0 brz-lh-lg-1_5 brz-lh-sm-im-1_4 brz-lh-xs-im-1_4 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ff-ubuntu brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-fs-lg-22 brz-fs-sm-im-21 brz-fs-xs-im-20 brz-css-ryQdO"><span class="brz-cp-color1">Purity</span></h5><p class="brz-lh-lg-1_3 brz-lh-sm-im-1_3 brz-lh-xs-im-1_3 brz-fs-lg-17 brz-fs-sm-im-16 brz-fs-xs-im-16 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ff-montserrat brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-css-tB95a"><span class="brz-cp-color7">Our high grade iron ore is assayed at 67% iron content. It is sold at a guaranteed 64% purity.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-68up2x brz-css-1xld67 brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-icon-text brz-css-3xyog0 brz-css-16u0wsn" data-brz-custom-id="xgupjuihbgkaoxadibcocourguzaiumnvhkq"><div class="brz-icon__container" data-brz-custom-id="umwenvussyctdgcyxdjgojklguuvmphrtbow"><span class="brz-icon brz-span brz-css-9ulzpx brz-css-fuqzm2"><svg class="brz-icon-svg align-[initial]"><use href="/wp-content/plugins/brizy/public/editor-build/prod/editor/icons/outline/tractor.svg#nc_icon"></use></svg></span></div><div class="brz-text-btn"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-1doei8y brz-css-1bhmuz4" data-brz-custom-id="eldmwzndoskwpeesjlqlglrmenolaoneexci"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><h5 class="brz-mb-lg-0 brz-lh-lg-1_5 brz-lh-sm-im-1_4 brz-lh-xs-im-1_4 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ff-ubuntu brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-fs-lg-22 brz-fs-sm-im-21 brz-fs-xs-im-20 brz-css-ignO0"><span class="brz-cp-color1">Production Capacity</span></h5><p class="brz-lh-lg-1_3 brz-lh-sm-im-1_3 brz-lh-xs-im-1_3 brz-fs-lg-17 brz-fs-sm-im-16 brz-fs-xs-im-16 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ff-montserrat brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-css-mB8wn"><span class="brz-cp-color7">Our productional capacity is currently at 500,000 MT / Month. This can be scaled for the right buyer. </span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-68up2x brz-css-o17fu3 brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-icon-text brz-css-3xyog0 brz-css-1oq4m8t" data-brz-custom-id="neibsqtnatnyxegtsdfxfsewrdfqumkcruku"><div class="brz-icon__container" data-brz-custom-id="drchodiqzxkhufgceybsgyvtymlrbqotttlc"><span class="brz-icon brz-span brz-css-9ulzpx brz-css-zr6rd5"><svg class="brz-icon-svg align-[initial]"><use href="/wp-content/plugins/brizy/public/editor-build/prod/editor/icons/outline/boat-front.svg#nc_icon"></use></svg></span></div><div class="brz-text-btn"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-1doei8y brz-css-1cfcitg" data-brz-custom-id="wgrwoaqeywlidnrtryydysewsdlkyahstscq"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><h5 class="brz-mb-lg-0 brz-lh-lg-1_5 brz-lh-sm-im-1_4 brz-lh-xs-im-1_4 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ff-ubuntu brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-fs-lg-22 brz-fs-sm-im-21 brz-fs-xs-im-20 brz-css-sF7aI"><span class="brz-cp-color1">Logistics</span></h5><p class="brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-lg-500 brz-ft-google brz-ff-montserrat brz-text-lg-justify brz-lh-lg-1_3 brz-lh-sm-im-1_3 brz-lh-xs-im-1_3 brz-fs-lg-17 brz-fs-sm-im-16 brz-fs-xs-im-16 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-text-sm-left brz-css-z7Cjg"><span class="brz-cp-color7">Our iron ore is typically shipped by ocean freight out of the port of Mati on the Island of Mindanao, Philippines. Shipping options of CIF and FOB are offered.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="brz-columns brz-css-o26tfp brz-css-1nd4cim" data-brz-custom-id="bucivwdxqibfkaejhcjfxpuqyvoiukstbllk"><div class="brz-bg"><div class="brz-bg-image"></div></div><div class="brz-column__items brz-css-1j8s0bo brz-css-1h2emzt"><div id="" class="brz-css-68up2x brz-css-1qwagqp brz-css-1v3ire0 brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-spacer brz-css-cnperg brz-css-16f6rso"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="copper" data-brz-id="ujlijcetknacxamnxtngjiqekcujokqiqwmj_ujlijcetknacxamnxtngjiqekcujokqiqwmj" class="brz-section brz-css-195q6zg brz-css-t0q2km"><div class="brz-section__content brz-section--boxed brz-css-1pca40u brz-css-sjqsy2" data-brz-custom-id="opgvlaasgfxauqzdltyldgtgvslbmvzpvjbl"><div class="brz-bg"><div class="brz-bg-color"></div><div class="brz-bg-shape brz-bg-shape__top"></div><div class="brz-bg-shape brz-bg-shape__bottom"></div></div><div class="brz-container brz-css-1a0szgz brz-css-1reb926"><div class="brz-row__container brz-css-1gvaz0f brz-css-87z5a3" data-brz-custom-id="cotmtzrmfpxbbaqclhqyctyiectuzvxjftgp"><div class="brz-row brz-css-17f88im brz-css-1f07eda brz-css-ne8am2"><div class="brz-columns brz-css-fj20m7 brz-css-nch4ss" data-brz-custom-id="gsoupmsbyfccriaeakekxpsswhihvlmmlovi"><div class="brz-column__items brz-css-1rwcs82 brz-css-1c137ex"><div id="" class="brz-css-1kt204m brz-css-1d3m49z brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-5uy21i brz-css-syygd1" data-brz-custom-id="wuqkdsoicglieszilikupaugpduxgkhradvc"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><h2 class="brz-text-xs-center brz-lh-lg-1_2 brz-lh-sm-im-1_2 brz-lh-xs-im-1_2 brz-fs-lg-42 brz-fs-sm-im-35 brz-fs-xs-im-30 brz-ls-lg-m_1_5 brz-ls-sm-im-m_0_5 brz-ls-xs-im-m_0_5 brz-ff-montserrat brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-700 brz-fw-sm-im-700 brz-fw-xs-im-700 brz-css-ehhBv"><span class="brz-cp-color8">Copper (Cu) </span></h2></div></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-1kt204m brz-css-v0fmly brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-5uy21i brz-css-1vdwhwl" data-brz-custom-id="oorbeizhikjzhqhcdmcnijfanvjupygpjysp"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><p class="brz-ls-xs-0 brz-fw-xs-400 brz-lh-xs-1_2 brz-fs-xs-16 brz-fw-lg-500 brz-text-xs-center brz-ff-ubuntu brz-ft-google brz-text-lg-justify brz-lh-sm-1_2 brz-fw-sm-400 brz-fs-sm-16 brz-ls-sm-0 brz-text-sm-left brz-fs-lg-22 brz-lh-lg-1_2 brz-ls-sm-im-m_1 brz-ls-xs-im-m_1 brz-ls-lg-m_1_5 brz-css-deCwx"><span class="brz-cp-color8">The primary&nbsp;applications of copper&nbsp;are in electrical wiring, roofing, plumbing, and industrial machinery. For most of these&nbsp;applications,&nbsp;copper&nbsp;is used in its pure form.</span></p></div></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-1kt204m brz-css-4mc0hx brz-css-1bed5ed brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-spacer brz-css-jlxbmu brz-css-1nu0s6m"></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-1kt204m brz-css-1brnh8u brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-icon-text brz-css-1l3g73a brz-css-h3ovic" data-brz-custom-id="qsvypppmoodioevurrtccexbcfsojjckxvyl"><div class="brz-icon__container" data-brz-custom-id="ppmjqmnwvbaofhrjkogosrkcdiufyxljmxza"><span class="brz-icon brz-span brz-css-bwbc3o brz-css-13epzbu"><svg class="brz-icon-svg align-[initial]"><use href="/wp-content/plugins/brizy/public/editor-build/prod/editor/icons/outline/scale-4.svg#nc_icon"></use></svg></span></div><div class="brz-text-btn"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-5uy21i brz-css-1jioshl" data-brz-custom-id="mgwoeratgrsmjagcsbhemujtyqhxcxqusenh"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><h5 class="brz-fs-xs-im-20 brz-fs-sm-im-21 brz-fs-lg-22 brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-lg-500 brz-ft-google brz-ff-ubuntu brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-lh-xs-im-1_4 brz-lh-sm-im-1_4 brz-lh-lg-1_5 brz-mb-lg-0 brz-css-kAnbA"><span class="brz-cp-color8">Purity</span></h5><p class="brz-fw-xs-im-300 brz-fw-sm-im-300 brz-fw-lg-300 brz-ft-google brz-ff-spinnaker brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-fs-xs-im-16 brz-fs-sm-im-16 brz-fs-lg-17 brz-lh-xs-im-1_3 brz-lh-sm-im-1_3 brz-lh-lg-1_3 brz-css-uhcpJ"><strong class="brz-cp-color7">Our Copper is derived from the processing of complex ore and sold as pure copper concentrate. </strong></p></div></div></div></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-1kt204m brz-css-jjki5s brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-icon-text brz-css-1l3g73a brz-css-11057a6" data-brz-custom-id="zllszwjdzxibgbqlcettagytgbruqeneabdq"><div class="brz-icon__container" data-brz-custom-id="zkarnpspsnubknsmnleelzucahzbftjwzqux"><span class="brz-icon brz-span brz-css-bwbc3o brz-css-xlkto3"><svg class="brz-icon-svg align-[initial]"><use href="/wp-content/plugins/brizy/public/editor-build/prod/editor/icons/outline/tractor.svg#nc_icon"></use></svg></span></div><div class="brz-text-btn"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-5uy21i brz-css-15lfh3p" data-brz-custom-id="tvzrwjudxpxpxvjahkrupjbntiagmuemavjb"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><h5 class="brz-mb-lg-0 brz-lh-lg-1_5 brz-lh-sm-im-1_4 brz-lh-xs-im-1_4 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ff-ubuntu brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-fs-lg-22 brz-fs-sm-im-21 brz-fs-xs-im-20 brz-css-wLyai"><span class="brz-cp-color8">Production Capacity</span></h5><p class="brz-lh-lg-1_3 brz-lh-sm-im-1_3 brz-lh-xs-im-1_3 brz-fs-lg-17 brz-fs-sm-im-16 brz-fs-xs-im-16 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ff-spinnaker brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-300 brz-fw-sm-im-300 brz-fw-xs-im-300 brz-css-uJCoa"><strong class="brz-cp-color7">Our productional capacity is currently at 2,000 MT / Month. </strong></p></div></div></div></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-1kt204m brz-css-1iottvc brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-icon-text brz-css-1l3g73a brz-css-l7mwwh" data-brz-custom-id="uacdvrmtxwzbxoidfkxwxmnnwcvjribnziaz"><div class="brz-icon__container" data-brz-custom-id="lyxfdfaccfhgpamoigirmlapucmflyvhrfwz"><span class="brz-icon brz-span brz-css-bwbc3o brz-css-2pmbha"><svg class="brz-icon-svg align-[initial]"><use href="/wp-content/plugins/brizy/public/editor-build/prod/editor/icons/outline/boat-front.svg#nc_icon"></use></svg></span></div><div class="brz-text-btn"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-5uy21i brz-css-1kdqbc6" data-brz-custom-id="whbopmhmcvpqiccpuvotlveuznosuxijswrt"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><h5 class="brz-fs-xs-im-20 brz-fs-sm-im-21 brz-fs-lg-22 brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-lg-500 brz-ft-google brz-ff-ubuntu brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-lh-xs-im-1_4 brz-lh-sm-im-1_4 brz-lh-lg-1_5 brz-mb-lg-0 brz-css-qu0UP"><span class="brz-cp-color8">Logistics</span></h5><p class="brz-ls-xs-im-m_1 brz-ls-lg-m_0_5 brz-text-lg-justify brz-fs-xs-im-16 brz-fs-sm-im-16 brz-fs-lg-17 brz-lh-xs-im-1_3 brz-lh-sm-im-1_3 brz-lh-lg-1_3 brz-ff-spinnaker brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-400 brz-fw-sm-im-400 brz-fw-xs-im-400 brz-ls-sm-m_0_5 brz-text-sm-left brz-css-mqZoD"><strong class="brz-cp-color7">Our iron ore is typically shipped by ocean freight out of the port of Mati on the Island of Mindanao, Philippines. Shipping options of CIF and FOB are offered.</strong></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="brz-columns brz-css-fj20m7 brz-css-yxmi9r" data-brz-custom-id="wzxoprnrrgdweolnvjqzqtvczwcsnbwowwyu"><div class="brz-bg"><div class="brz-bg-image"></div></div><div class="brz-column__items brz-css-1rwcs82 brz-css-ai1pic"><div id="" class="brz-css-1kt204m brz-css-4mc0hx brz-css-dep4pb brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-spacer brz-css-jlxbmu brz-css-gte8bv"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="gold" data-brz-id="exihtvcfnbdlbuplgcfjjutepfnkigcbjbye_exihtvcfnbdlbuplgcfjjutepfnkigcbjbye" class="brz-section brz-css-vxt3mm brz-css-lbb2p5"><div class="brz-section__content brz-section--boxed brz-css-1i3vryx brz-css-118042s" data-brz-custom-id="fysxushgkmftxdtqttpuobpaizrepochvtpu"><div class="brz-bg"><div class="brz-bg-color"></div></div><div class="brz-container brz-css-hq94ee brz-css-t415yc"><div class="brz-row__container brz-css-jhlyym brz-css-pe9ayl" data-brz-custom-id="bvkpxdervicgeullnqvkvrwedmncpbnetspi"><div class="brz-row brz-css-1ix61lv brz-css-1clqfdw brz-css-1eiivhh"><div class="brz-columns brz-css-n6qcjr brz-css-8uttyl" data-brz-custom-id="flmrucirhordbdgfmnfkctfrjtgfcpquavro"><div class="brz-column__items brz-css-1wlqz2q brz-css-y62b1e"><div id="" class="brz-css-go2w9o brz-css-1m5s5jj brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-hhyrai brz-css-byuksx" data-brz-custom-id="dyjtpxaiyfuwcsnzfusgmdrzifaarlihsvfc"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><h2 class="brz-fw-xs-im-700 brz-fw-sm-im-700 brz-fw-lg-700 brz-ft-google brz-ff-montserrat brz-ls-xs-im-m_0_5 brz-ls-sm-im-m_0_5 brz-ls-lg-m_1_5 brz-fs-xs-im-30 brz-fs-sm-im-35 brz-fs-lg-42 brz-lh-xs-im-1_2 brz-lh-sm-im-1_2 brz-lh-lg-1_2 brz-text-xs-center brz-css-qmmHs"><span class="brz-cp-color1">Gold (Au)</span></h2></div></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-go2w9o brz-css-zvg83y brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-hhyrai brz-css-f6j0hx" data-brz-custom-id="tkkqvjmdlzkatynxsjbkawozbavoidprmnfa"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><p class="brz-ls-xs-0 brz-fw-xs-400 brz-lh-xs-1_2 brz-fs-xs-16 brz-text-xs-center brz-ff-ubuntu brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-300 brz-text-lg-justify brz-fs-sm-16 brz-lh-sm-1_2 brz-fw-sm-400 brz-ls-sm-0 brz-text-sm-left brz-fs-lg-22 brz-lh-lg-1_2 brz-ls-lg-m_1_5 brz-ls-sm-im-m_2 brz-ls-xs-im-m_2 brz-css-uSgTn"><span class="brz-cp-color1">Iron ore&nbsp;is the main source of pure iron&nbsp;for the world's&nbsp;iron&nbsp;and steel industries... It is therefore&nbsp;essential&nbsp;for the production of steel, which in turn is&nbsp;essential&nbsp;to maintain a strong industrial base. Almost all (98%)&nbsp;iron ore&nbsp;is used in steelmaking.</span></p></div></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-go2w9o brz-css-1nfek23 brz-css-1g26dus brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-spacer brz-css-tkxbab brz-css-q02joz"></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-go2w9o brz-css-eiiebb brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-icon-text brz-css-z8v6u0 brz-css-t8weba" data-brz-custom-id="aloqwyxphrkreuoigxbvckgypvzboahakzxj"><div class="brz-icon__container" data-brz-custom-id="ahcpwnmblhbnpqnvgqhvpxgdadekborelktf"><span class="brz-icon brz-span brz-css-1ult2x0 brz-css-14q1gym"><svg class="brz-icon-svg align-[initial]"><use href="/wp-content/plugins/brizy/public/editor-build/prod/editor/icons/outline/scale-4.svg#nc_icon"></use></svg></span></div><div class="brz-text-btn"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-hhyrai brz-css-14lxk7x" data-brz-custom-id="njgofjmmvzdvfdcghxdizycsixxlrpsyvyvo"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><h5 class="brz-mb-lg-0 brz-lh-lg-1_5 brz-lh-sm-im-1_4 brz-lh-xs-im-1_4 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ff-ubuntu brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-fs-lg-22 brz-fs-sm-im-21 brz-fs-xs-im-20 brz-css-okWO9"><span class="brz-cp-color1">Purity</span></h5><p class="brz-lh-lg-1_3 brz-lh-sm-im-1_3 brz-lh-xs-im-1_3 brz-fs-lg-17 brz-fs-sm-im-16 brz-fs-xs-im-16 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ff-montserrat brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-css-zSqEk"><span class="brz-cp-color7">Our high grade iron ore is assayed at 67% iron content. It is sold at a guaranteed 64% purity.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-go2w9o brz-css-wrnriu brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-icon-text brz-css-z8v6u0 brz-css-1gqdv8k" data-brz-custom-id="hfgeqvzrihywjwqdxwfjhcxhnamftsitamet"><div class="brz-icon__container" data-brz-custom-id="byavtoralffoisrxcnvkigkadhifisjmhaqr"><span class="brz-icon brz-span brz-css-1ult2x0 brz-css-7x4rje"><svg class="brz-icon-svg align-[initial]"><use href="/wp-content/plugins/brizy/public/editor-build/prod/editor/icons/outline/tractor.svg#nc_icon"></use></svg></span></div><div class="brz-text-btn"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-hhyrai brz-css-1nyi2qf" data-brz-custom-id="naaplwbqugnscdggnrjmfysfsytdnhfwhyke"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><h5 class="brz-mb-lg-0 brz-lh-lg-1_5 brz-lh-sm-im-1_4 brz-lh-xs-im-1_4 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ff-ubuntu brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-fs-lg-22 brz-fs-sm-im-21 brz-fs-xs-im-20 brz-css-i_cB8"><span class="brz-cp-color1">Production Capacity</span></h5><p class="brz-lh-lg-1_3 brz-lh-sm-im-1_3 brz-lh-xs-im-1_3 brz-fs-lg-17 brz-fs-sm-im-16 brz-fs-xs-im-16 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ff-montserrat brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-css-mpjLX"><span class="brz-cp-color7">Our productional capacity is currently at 500,000 MT / Month. This can be scaled for the right buyer. </span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-go2w9o brz-css-iepw3x brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-icon-text brz-css-z8v6u0 brz-css-17ahx3i" data-brz-custom-id="menobcboahmjyptgwppbzyqkfrxhcgpqgran"><div class="brz-icon__container" data-brz-custom-id="iewwnjvzltzuwtwbricwftnpzmmwzxohrkbm"><span class="brz-icon brz-span brz-css-1ult2x0 brz-css-10ldujk"><svg class="brz-icon-svg align-[initial]"><use href="/wp-content/plugins/brizy/public/editor-build/prod/editor/icons/outline/boat-front.svg#nc_icon"></use></svg></span></div><div class="brz-text-btn"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-hhyrai brz-css-fjppo8" data-brz-custom-id="zkojzyckplqltqpwcvbzyeprmcjvvnhyxrys"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><h5 class="brz-mb-lg-0 brz-lh-lg-1_5 brz-lh-sm-im-1_4 brz-lh-xs-im-1_4 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ff-ubuntu brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-fs-lg-22 brz-fs-sm-im-21 brz-fs-xs-im-20 brz-css-pQ2jw"><span class="brz-cp-color1">Logistics</span></h5><p class="brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-lg-500 brz-ft-google brz-ff-montserrat brz-text-lg-justify brz-lh-lg-1_3 brz-lh-sm-im-1_3 brz-lh-xs-im-1_3 brz-fs-lg-17 brz-fs-sm-im-16 brz-fs-xs-im-16 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-text-sm-left brz-css-ckdna"><span class="brz-cp-color7">Our iron ore is typically shipped by ocean freight out of the port of Mati on the Island of Mindanao, Philippines. Shipping options of CIF and FOB are offered.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="brz-columns brz-css-n6qcjr brz-css-dxzixl" data-brz-custom-id="kvswamzkrdnlyljupnzfghntcqauhkzbqzxm"><div class="brz-bg"><div class="brz-bg-image"></div></div><div class="brz-column__items brz-css-1wlqz2q brz-css-4ffgpw"><div id="" class="brz-css-go2w9o brz-css-1nfek23 brz-css-kpnb8g brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-spacer brz-css-tkxbab brz-css-1lf1dfq"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="silica" data-brz-id="pwwlondaeqiynputmdgwciosrtzevzrphypz_pwwlondaeqiynputmdgwciosrtzevzrphypz" class="brz-section brz-css-b3ui1u brz-css-85d1y"><div class="brz-section__content brz-section--boxed brz-css-szjcai brz-css-2pcciq" data-brz-custom-id="ymstxeyeaxygiigaheybatdnalexvenvjrrh"><div class="brz-bg"><div class="brz-bg-color"></div><div class="brz-bg-shape brz-bg-shape__top"></div><div class="brz-bg-shape brz-bg-shape__bottom"></div></div><div class="brz-container brz-css-qd5ifz brz-css-17ezrbj"><div class="brz-row__container brz-css-gu6w7y brz-css-ll65xs" data-brz-custom-id="pzbcjilromntrxrglcqjqxewbilpzdphnzzj"><div class="brz-row brz-css-ymlah5 brz-css-1u120ak brz-css-9grzrk"><div class="brz-columns brz-css-4cqw6o brz-css-18veo4x" data-brz-custom-id="bvobqnrrnguccmfclyxjwfaddgbinhoiikpe"><div class="brz-column__items brz-css-o9wyd6 brz-css-1mfpd10"><div id="" class="brz-css-14xvljh brz-css-12epcf3 brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-7kq6ie brz-css-1wbec1f" data-brz-custom-id="bedyitbnqfrhmvwkizrdmgqspkduyhfszfym"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><h2 class="brz-fw-xs-im-700 brz-fw-sm-im-700 brz-fw-lg-700 brz-ft-google brz-ff-montserrat brz-ls-xs-im-m_0_5 brz-ls-sm-im-m_0_5 brz-ls-lg-m_1_5 brz-fs-xs-im-30 brz-fs-sm-im-35 brz-fs-lg-42 brz-lh-xs-im-1_2 brz-lh-sm-im-1_2 brz-lh-lg-1_2 brz-text-xs-center brz-css-t1I3s"><span class="brz-cp-color8">Silica (Si) </span></h2></div></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-14xvljh brz-css-12uxkit brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-7kq6ie brz-css-1d5o3pp" data-brz-custom-id="dqhxntoqgmrmxvrgrxcrjhiijcetzoeidgmy"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><p class="brz-ls-xs-0 brz-fw-xs-400 brz-lh-xs-1_2 brz-fs-xs-16 brz-fw-lg-500 brz-text-xs-center brz-ff-ubuntu brz-ft-google brz-text-lg-justify brz-fs-sm-16 brz-lh-sm-1_2 brz-fw-sm-400 brz-ls-sm-0 brz-text-sm-left brz-fs-lg-22 brz-lh-lg-1_2 brz-ls-sm-im-m_1 brz-ls-xs-im-m_1 brz-ls-lg-m_1_5 brz-css-fN16_"><span class="brz-cp-color8">The primary&nbsp;applications of copper&nbsp;are in electrical wiring, roofing, plumbing, and industrial machinery. For most of these&nbsp;applications,&nbsp;copper&nbsp;is used in its pure form.</span></p></div></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-14xvljh brz-css-ka7t4n brz-css-i72jmz brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-spacer brz-css-nneydi brz-css-872zny"></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-14xvljh brz-css-nq0f8z brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-icon-text brz-css-8z1ei7 brz-css-1brr58m" data-brz-custom-id="qwzhswyyxvpnjpzloiuikbuhngaamjzvtofv"><div class="brz-icon__container" data-brz-custom-id="qnmuhldliewnwjuzacnxtclymeuwcefhtpil"><span class="brz-icon brz-span brz-css-jjpak7 brz-css-1qjkgcm"><svg class="brz-icon-svg align-[initial]"><use href="/wp-content/plugins/brizy/public/editor-build/prod/editor/icons/outline/scale-4.svg#nc_icon"></use></svg></span></div><div class="brz-text-btn"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-7kq6ie brz-css-1djygvb" data-brz-custom-id="dqmduzkgpsdlohkblgjlxrpazmessixbzvhk"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><h5 class="brz-fs-xs-im-20 brz-fs-sm-im-21 brz-fs-lg-22 brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-lg-500 brz-ft-google brz-ff-ubuntu brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-lh-xs-im-1_4 brz-lh-sm-im-1_4 brz-lh-lg-1_5 brz-mb-lg-0 brz-css-toCcM"><span class="brz-cp-color8">Purity</span></h5><p class="brz-fw-xs-im-300 brz-fw-sm-im-300 brz-fw-lg-300 brz-ft-google brz-ff-spinnaker brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-fs-xs-im-16 brz-fs-sm-im-16 brz-fs-lg-17 brz-lh-xs-im-1_3 brz-lh-sm-im-1_3 brz-lh-lg-1_3 brz-css-uDisl"><strong class="brz-cp-color7">Our Copper is derived from the processing of complex ore and sold as pure copper concentrate. </strong></p></div></div></div></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-14xvljh brz-css-3auajy brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-icon-text brz-css-8z1ei7 brz-css-1sersxg" data-brz-custom-id="bplospvzmapqdsbgvthioealkdbwqcmwvjfr"><div class="brz-icon__container" data-brz-custom-id="jrhmqvypjlpnnfjqjxubqzrigclvedknxurj"><span class="brz-icon brz-span brz-css-jjpak7 brz-css-lbrl39"><svg class="brz-icon-svg align-[initial]"><use href="/wp-content/plugins/brizy/public/editor-build/prod/editor/icons/outline/tractor.svg#nc_icon"></use></svg></span></div><div class="brz-text-btn"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-7kq6ie brz-css-h8ugny" data-brz-custom-id="lfmlbafiiunotvoryipklscgbslckcrbxqcx"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><h5 class="brz-mb-lg-0 brz-lh-lg-1_5 brz-lh-sm-im-1_4 brz-lh-xs-im-1_4 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ff-ubuntu brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-fs-lg-22 brz-fs-sm-im-21 brz-fs-xs-im-20 brz-css-aN9BC"><span class="brz-cp-color8">Production Capacity</span></h5><p class="brz-lh-lg-1_3 brz-lh-sm-im-1_3 brz-lh-xs-im-1_3 brz-fs-lg-17 brz-fs-sm-im-16 brz-fs-xs-im-16 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ff-spinnaker brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-300 brz-fw-sm-im-300 brz-fw-xs-im-300 brz-css-ceXu9"><strong class="brz-cp-color7">Our productional capacity is currently at 2,000 MT / Month. </strong></p></div></div></div></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-14xvljh brz-css-gq37iz brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-icon-text brz-css-8z1ei7 brz-css-jyc5eh" data-brz-custom-id="orotwkttcmewkxmpdmvnrephtdjdneiykhgr"><div class="brz-icon__container" data-brz-custom-id="jgbbkxpwvjfpgcdiynzgtnbtmcqzxzvvmirg"><span class="brz-icon brz-span brz-css-jjpak7 brz-css-da6838"><svg class="brz-icon-svg align-[initial]"><use href="/wp-content/plugins/brizy/public/editor-build/prod/editor/icons/outline/boat-front.svg#nc_icon"></use></svg></span></div><div class="brz-text-btn"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-7kq6ie brz-css-1m2ysvm" data-brz-custom-id="xveflfgzlxcdbanoqdzktlnzbsigjqymiapj"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><h5 class="brz-fs-xs-im-20 brz-fs-sm-im-21 brz-fs-lg-22 brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-lg-500 brz-ft-google brz-ff-ubuntu brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-lh-xs-im-1_4 brz-lh-sm-im-1_4 brz-lh-lg-1_5 brz-mb-lg-0 brz-css-nBqCv"><span class="brz-cp-color8">Logistics</span></h5><p class="brz-ls-xs-im-m_1 brz-ls-sm-im-m_1 brz-ls-lg-m_0_5 brz-text-lg-justify brz-fs-xs-im-16 brz-fs-sm-im-16 brz-fs-lg-17 brz-lh-xs-im-1_3 brz-lh-sm-im-1_3 brz-lh-lg-1_3 brz-ff-spinnaker brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-400 brz-fw-sm-im-400 brz-fw-xs-im-400 brz-text-sm-left brz-css-rsgCU"><strong class="brz-cp-color7">Our iron ore is typically shipped by ocean freight out of the port of Mati on the Island of Mindanao, Philippines. Shipping options of CIF and FOB are offered.</strong></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="brz-columns brz-css-4cqw6o brz-css-oe8cp9" data-brz-custom-id="rpqjwbpibyrgcdrsmpmhxtjonfhzmtunfdng"><div class="brz-bg"><div class="brz-bg-image"></div></div><div class="brz-column__items brz-css-o9wyd6 brz-css-bxhvni"><div id="" class="brz-css-14xvljh brz-css-ka7t4n brz-css-hglzv1 brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-spacer brz-css-nneydi brz-css-1caso61"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="gypsum" data-brz-id="fjcxiufbevcdgiwjsccjcrfjvnsvnuojrseo_fjcxiufbevcdgiwjsccjcrfjvnsvnuojrseo" class="brz-section brz-css-141920f brz-css-1l0gcvc"><div class="brz-section__content brz-section--boxed brz-css-1dj0hz1 brz-css-iud8io" data-brz-custom-id="ulsvqtmbmzlnmuqlenfnuvmmqyneifriwkti"><div class="brz-bg"><div class="brz-bg-color"></div></div><div class="brz-container brz-css-8akozr brz-css-fw6zhi"><div class="brz-row__container brz-css-rnyimt brz-css-1q9w807" data-brz-custom-id="iveiwodjjxfvsrctzitxgdykwccyhbqxlkuk"><div class="brz-row brz-css-1t77k42 brz-css-xat94j brz-css-xibme8"><div class="brz-columns brz-css-4ywx22 brz-css-l02z4r" data-brz-custom-id="djxqisnozdopvoyayykmacgipxwgcytilqsf"><div class="brz-column__items brz-css-qt2bkh brz-css-ch14ah"><div id="" class="brz-css-1z12alr brz-css-wr1feu brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-1g5l87b brz-css-otlhdz" data-brz-custom-id="tolxqrwgyjrxkmcesfsmfjxtihsrubdorhka"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><h2 class="brz-text-xs-center brz-lh-lg-1_2 brz-lh-sm-im-1_2 brz-lh-xs-im-1_2 brz-fs-lg-42 brz-fs-sm-im-35 brz-fs-xs-im-30 brz-ls-lg-m_1_5 brz-ls-sm-im-m_0_5 brz-ls-xs-im-m_0_5 brz-ff-montserrat brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-700 brz-fw-sm-im-700 brz-fw-xs-im-700 brz-css-zuftR"><span class="brz-cp-color1">Gypsum (CaSO4)</span></h2></div></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-1z12alr brz-css-1ve16n3 brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-1g5l87b brz-css-13nc60" data-brz-custom-id="nbyjsrxhtkzcxzatvqixjscvdfqtayismlqh"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><p class="brz-ls-xs-0 brz-fw-xs-400 brz-lh-xs-1_2 brz-fs-xs-16 brz-text-lg-justify brz-fw-lg-300 brz-ft-google brz-ff-ubuntu brz-text-xs-center brz-fs-sm-16 brz-lh-sm-1_2 brz-fw-sm-400 brz-ls-sm-0 brz-text-sm-left brz-fs-lg-22 brz-lh-lg-1_2 brz-ls-lg-m_1 brz-ls-sm-im-m_1 brz-ls-xs-im-m_1 brz-css-gcEkJ"><span class="brz-cp-color1">Gypsum uses include: manufacture of wallboard, cement, plaster of Paris,&nbsp;soil conditioning, a hardening retarder in portland cement. </span></p></div></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-1z12alr brz-css-16vk3ai brz-css-1moem0p brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-spacer brz-css-ce0gys brz-css-11zyhk7"></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-1z12alr brz-css-1a620gb brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-icon-text brz-css-yyhycm brz-css-1jqzw1l" data-brz-custom-id="cdbsmvpblqoilbixyhzpdbtjvzyziemnsklx"><div class="brz-icon__container" data-brz-custom-id="mtzkpoqwijsmimhgmiscofutjrlznzicdtxl"><span class="brz-icon brz-span brz-css-1e1dvg5 brz-css-ayevt1"><svg class="brz-icon-svg align-[initial]"><use href="/wp-content/plugins/brizy/public/editor-build/prod/editor/icons/outline/scale-4.svg#nc_icon"></use></svg></span></div><div class="brz-text-btn"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-1g5l87b brz-css-5mjmzd" data-brz-custom-id="fmnqlsnvltkdpousjhyrkfakbmwvmbqvjbvf"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><h5 class="brz-mb-lg-0 brz-lh-lg-1_5 brz-lh-sm-im-1_4 brz-lh-xs-im-1_4 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ff-ubuntu brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-fs-lg-22 brz-fs-sm-im-21 brz-fs-xs-im-20 brz-css-dub4C"><span class="brz-cp-color1">Purity</span></h5><p class="brz-lh-lg-1_3 brz-lh-sm-im-1_3 brz-lh-xs-im-1_3 brz-fs-lg-17 brz-fs-sm-im-16 brz-fs-xs-im-16 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ff-montserrat brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-css-vP_ar"><span class="brz-cp-color7">Our high grade iron ore is assayed at 67% iron content. It is sold at a guaranteed 64% purity.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-1z12alr brz-css-1a53twm brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-icon-text brz-css-yyhycm brz-css-1od4d0w" data-brz-custom-id="cvkohqjtpfkypojwunltaafnyozqhqoeeawz"><div class="brz-icon__container" data-brz-custom-id="icaseryvgqwbbsnvhrmpyumqfvmltltoosof"><span class="brz-icon brz-span brz-css-1e1dvg5 brz-css-64tfzn"><svg class="brz-icon-svg align-[initial]"><use href="/wp-content/plugins/brizy/public/editor-build/prod/editor/icons/outline/tractor.svg#nc_icon"></use></svg></span></div><div class="brz-text-btn"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-1g5l87b brz-css-1phevpr" data-brz-custom-id="gvkjwsawhfcresfmiqdvlpilpfjrhpxvmnky"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><h5 class="brz-mb-lg-0 brz-lh-lg-1_5 brz-lh-sm-im-1_4 brz-lh-xs-im-1_4 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ff-ubuntu brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-fs-lg-22 brz-fs-sm-im-21 brz-fs-xs-im-20 brz-css-lLTex"><span class="brz-cp-color1">Production Capacity</span></h5><p class="brz-lh-lg-1_3 brz-lh-sm-im-1_3 brz-lh-xs-im-1_3 brz-fs-lg-17 brz-fs-sm-im-16 brz-fs-xs-im-16 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ff-montserrat brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-css-u7kpy"><span class="brz-cp-color7">Our productional capacity is currently at 500,000 MT / Month. This can be scaled for the right buyer. </span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div id="" class="brz-css-1z12alr brz-css-136n0wq brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-icon-text brz-css-yyhycm brz-css-ayaeva" data-brz-custom-id="incvyqywyzbbduadqodpjrygmzveptumbtjb"><div class="brz-icon__container" data-brz-custom-id="uhairdvkvfiariljuhcpsstvtqwofjxbguah"><span class="brz-icon brz-span brz-css-1e1dvg5 brz-css-1txoajo"><svg class="brz-icon-svg align-[initial]"><use href="/wp-content/plugins/brizy/public/editor-build/prod/editor/icons/outline/boat-front.svg#nc_icon"></use></svg></span></div><div class="brz-text-btn"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-rich-text__custom brz-css-1g5l87b brz-css-1c8f4fe" data-brz-custom-id="nsawvbeigdgmgiwsrmhnjrodojyfzljeviau"><div data-brz-translate-text="1"><h5 class="brz-mb-lg-0 brz-lh-lg-1_5 brz-lh-sm-im-1_4 brz-lh-xs-im-1_4 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ff-ubuntu brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-fs-lg-22 brz-fs-sm-im-21 brz-fs-xs-im-20 brz-css-c7426"><span class="brz-cp-color1">Logistics</span></h5><p class="brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-lg-500 brz-ft-google brz-ff-montserrat brz-text-lg-justify brz-lh-lg-1_3 brz-lh-sm-im-1_3 brz-lh-xs-im-1_3 brz-fs-lg-17 brz-fs-sm-im-16 brz-fs-xs-im-16 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-text-sm-left brz-css-rx73G"><span class="brz-cp-color7">Our iron ore is typically shipped by ocean freight out of the port of Mati on the Island of Mindanao, Philippines. Shipping options of CIF and FOB are offered.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="brz-columns brz-css-4ywx22 brz-css-1x5frt1" data-brz-custom-id="bylqpizfuqkyfdgyvavtzvhjiawnbqvtgupo"><div class="brz-bg"><div class="brz-bg-image"></div></div><div class="brz-column__items brz-css-qt2bkh brz-css-6nfgkq"><div id="" class="brz-css-1z12alr brz-css-16vk3ai brz-css-3j21aw brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-spacer brz-css-ce0gys brz-css-6oqjts"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="limestone" data-brz-id="ipwmedhlismjfevlaajfuofzkspqbmvbuykf_ipwmedhlismjfevlaajfuofzkspqbmvbuykf" class="brz-section brz-css-1374nqt brz-css-wjefat"><div class="brz-section__content brz-section--boxed brz-css-1o500x9 brz-css-9n59x9" data-brz-custom-id="kxyrdwkkrjbdziqawwxjrtcaikfxylitptfy"><div class="brz-bg"><div class="brz-bg-color"></div><div class="brz-bg-shape brz-bg-shape__top"></div><div class="brz-bg-shape brz-bg-shape__bottom"></div></div><div class="brz-container brz-css-by36c5 brz-css-1473wfu"><div class="brz-row__container brz-css-1cy6cxv brz-css-1g8d03e"